src/machdata/*
--------------
  Representation of entities and computation of some standard entities.

  entity.doc:	Description of entity representation.
  entity.h:	Definitions for entity representation.
		There are two forms, described in sment.h and lgent.h.
		Only one form is used -- see options.h to select the
		form.
  sment.h:	Description of entities as represented in the compact form.
  lgent.h:	Description of entities as represented in the larger form.
  gc.h:		Description and definitions for marking during
		garbage collection.
  smgc.h:	Specifics of gc.h for compact entities.
  lggc.h:	Specifics of gc.h for larger entities.
  entity.c:	Computation of some standard entities.
  except.h:	Standard exceptions.
  except.c: 	Trapping, exception naming.
  wrap.c:	Handling of entity wrapping and unwrapping.


